ActCanadian Commercial Corporation Act
PrecisAppointment of ERNEST B. BRIARD of Ottawa, Ontario, to be interim President of the Canadian Commercial Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months, or until such time as a new President is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective November 3, 2020.
